&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in managing and supporting Workday HCM systems in a large-scale, multi-entity environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong

